&lt;p&gt;30th Street Animal Hospital is hiring an &lt;strong&gt;experienced&lt;/strong&gt; full-time small-animal Veterinarian to provide comprehensive medical, surgical, and dental care to a variety of animal patients. Sorry, no new grads at this time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What to Expect&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
