&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paid time off.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Catch your breath with paid holidays, days of PTO, plus paid CE days every year. Take the time you need to recharge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partnership opportunities through Veterinary Practice Partners (VPP),&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;where more than 235 vets co-own practices across 177 locations. VPP offers unmatched support in operations, marketing, and finance, allowing you to focus on your passion for veterinary medicine.&lt;/li&gt;
